Consider the following instance variable and method.

```
private int[] array;

/** Precondition: array.length > 0
 */

public int checkArray() {
  int loc = 0;
  for (int k = 1; k < array.length; k++) {
    if (array[k] < array[loc]) {
      loc = k;
    }
  }

    return loc;
}
```

